item.title: CVE-2022-1743|2024-09-16T18:03:09.846Z -- dominion%20voting%20system -- imagecast%20x%20application
item.description: The tested version of Dominion Voting System ImageCast X can be manipulated to cause arbitrary code execution by specially crafted election definition files. An attacker could leverage this vulnerability to spread malicious code to ImageCast X devices from the EMS.
